cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DB 

Reasoning: 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is the most likely category as the paper deals with relevance feedback in search. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper introduces a timeline interface to help users adjust their feedback. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a Bayesian regression model for predicting the accuracy of user feedback. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is possible as the paper deals with natural language feedback. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also possible as the paper deals with managing and analyzing feedback data.
